+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| 1. Introduction
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
  The OpenFlow Swtich contains hardware datapath implemented on NetFPGA-CML,
and software openflow-agent implemented on PC. NetFPGA-CML is plugged into 
PC with PCI-e interface. Hardware datapath matains Flow Table to make forwarding
decision, as well as Flow Table can be modified by controller through OpenFlow Prot.
OpenFlow agent is responsible to translate OpenFlow protocol to specific operation
on hardware.
   __________________
  |    Controller    |
  |__________________|
  OpenFlow | Protocol
   ________↓_________
  |  OpenFlow-Agent  |
  |  Hardware Library|
  |  Driver          |
  |__________________|
      PCIe | 
   ________↓_________
  |    Datapath      |
  |__________________|
Fig. Full System Overview

